how to use R to perform simple linear regression to generate a model and test the slope
Scatter plot: ggplot(data=…aes(x= , y=))+geom_point()+geom_smooth(method= “lm”)

Linear regression function: model <- lm(y~x, data=  )
                             Summary(model)

how to use R to perform multiple regression to generate a model and test the slopes
